The Information Mode

     When it is desirable to obtain more information about the current
     sector than the standard conquer display provides,  the  informa­
     tion  mode is what you are looking for.  To enter the information
     mode, simply use  the  "toggle-infomode"  command,  and  it  will
     switch  between  the standard conquer display and the information
     mode.

     The information mode is very much like the standard conquer  dis­
     play, but the map takes up much less of the screen, and the extra
     space is filled by a section which will show as much  information
     about  the  sector  as  the  nation knows.  The right side of the
     screen is then totally devoted to the listing of the troops with­
     in the sector.

